**Overview**

The Gmail dashboard includes a variety of visualizations that highlight different activities performed in Gmail. It features components such as a bar charts displaying the top senders, top recipients and the most frequent attachment types, a bar chart analyzing the most commonly triggered custom rules, a bar char analyzing trends in spam classification over time, and a line chart tracking event trends over time. These insights help administrators understand user behavior, monitor system events, ensure data security, and assess the usage of various data sources within the workspace.
